==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interment
<hw>In*ter"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>enterment</ets>, F. <ets>enterrement</ets>. See <er>Inter</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>The act or ceremony of depositing a dead
body in the earth; burial; sepulture; inhumation.</def> <rj><au>T.
Warton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

